description: List all tunnels for an Amazon Web Services account. Tunnels are listed by creation time in descending order, newer tunnels will be listed before older tunnels. Requires permission to access the ListTunnels action.

nested_items.name: tunnelSummaries
nested_items.description: A short description of the tunnels in an Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: tunnelId
nested_items.description: The unique alpha-numeric identifier for the tunnel.

nested_items.name: tunnelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name of the tunnel.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of a tunnel. Valid values are: Open and Closed.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time the tunnel was created.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The time the tunnel was last updated.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use to get the next set of results, or null if there are no additional results.
